details.biography:
Jennie Kwan (born September 9, 1973) is an American television, film, and voice actress. She played Samantha "Sam" Woo on California Dreams, Satoko Hojo in Higurashi When They Cry, and voiced Suki, a character on Avatar: The Last Airbender.
